格蘭德的首張錄音室專輯《[[真情歌_(亞莉安娜·格蘭德專輯)|真情歌]]》發行於2013年9月3日，並得到了一致的好評。一個月後，格蘭德在《[[滾石_(雜誌)|滾石]]》的一次專訪中表示，她已經開始寫歌並籌備她的第二張錄音室專輯，且已經完成了兩首歌曲。<ref name="Extension" />錄音工作於2013年10月展開，由格蘭德前一張專輯的製作人[[哈爾默尼·薩謬斯|哈爾默尼·薩謬斯]]與湯米·布朗操刀。<ref>{{cite web|title=Ariana Grande Twitter announces she's working on second album in studio|url=http://www.musictimes.com/articles/3392/20140113/ariana-grande-twitter-announces-shes-working-second-album-studio.htm|publisher=Music Times|date=2014-01-13|first=Carolyn|last=Menyes|accessdate=2014-11-18|archive-date=2019-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190405004711/https://www.musictimes.com/articles/3392/20140113/ariana-grande-twitter-announces-shes-working-second-album-studio.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Ridiculous">{{cite web|last1=Joanne|first1=Dorke|title=Ariana Grande Confirms New Song 'Ridiculous'|url=http://www.mtv.co.uk/ariana-grande/news/ariana-grande-confirms-new-song-ridiculous|website=MTV News UK|date=2013-10-13|accessdate=2014-11-18|archive-date=2019-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402115430/http://www.mtv.co.uk/ariana-grande/news/ariana-grande-confirms-new-song-ridiculous|dead-url=no}}</ref>格蘭德最初計劃在2014年2月左右發行這張專輯。<ref>{{cite web|title=Ariana Grande Starts Working On Her Second Album|url=http://www.disneydreaming.com/2013/10/31/ariana-grande-starts-working-on-her-second-album/|work=Disneydreaming.com|date=2013-10-31|first=Disney Dreaming|accessdate=2014-11-18|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203014804/http://www.disneydreaming.com/2013/10/31/ariana-grande-starts-working-on-her-second-album/|archivedate=2013-12-03}}</ref>之後她於2014年1月證實，她已經與新的製作人[[萊恩·特德|萊恩·特德]]、[[薩文·科特查|薩文·科特查]]、[[班尼·布蘭科|班尼·布蘭科]]、基·万和[[馬克斯·馬丁|馬克斯·馬丁]]合作。<ref>{{cite web|last=Lee|first=Christina|title=Ariana Grande Talks Working With Max Martin For Second Album|url=http://www.idolator.com/7503309/ariana-grande-second-album-producers-max-martin|publisher=SpinMedia|date=2014-01-27|accessdate=2014-11-18|archive-date=2021-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210221010218/https://www.idolator.com/7503309/ariana-grande-second-album-producers-max-martin|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Fox|first=Sarah|title=Ariana Grande back to work in the studio, recording second album|url=http://theslanted.com/2014/01/12960/ariana-grande-back-to-work-in-the-studio-recording-second-album/|publisher=Grimm Media Publications LLC|date=2014-01-13|accessdate=2014-11-18|archive-date=2019-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629065828/https://theslanted.com/2014/01/12960/ariana-grande-back-to-work-in-the-studio-recording-second-album/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Lipshutz|first1=Jason|title=Ariana Grande Talks 'Problem' Single & Second Album, Due Out August/September|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6070079/ariana-grande-talks-problem-single-second-album-due-out|website=Billboard|date=2014-04-28|accessdate=2014-11-18|archive-date=2014-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140501095225/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6070079/ariana-grande-talks-problem-single-second-album-due-out|dead-url=no}}</ref>格蘭德在2月底表示，她想要以一首在當周末完成的真誠且令她流淚的歌曲，來命名她的新專輯。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Grande|first1=Ariana|title=progress update! I think I want to name the album...|url=https://www.facebook.com/arianagrande/posts/10151965028436027?stream_ref=10|website=Facebook|date=2014-02-25|accessdate=2014-11-18|archive-date=2020-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200808073045/https://www.facebook.com/arianagrande/posts/10151965028436027?stream_ref=10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Smith|first1=Carl|title=Ariana Grande Teases Her Second Album: "It's Very Special and Honest'|url=http://www.sugarscape.com/main-topics/music/1020852/ariana-grande-teases-her-second-album-its-very-special-and-honest|website=Sugar Scape|date=2014-02-25|accessdate=2014-11-18|archive-date=2014-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141020003301/http://www.sugarscape.com/main-topics/music/1020852/ariana-grande-teases-her-second-album-its-very-special-and-honest|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2014年3月3日的消息指出，格蘭德將會在克里斯小子即將發行的第六張錄音室專輯《[[X檔案_(克里斯小子專輯)|X檔案]]》，與他合作第五支單曲《Don't Be Gone Too Long》。<ref>{{cite web|last=Wass|first=Mike|title=Ariana Grande’s Duet With Chris Brown Is Apparently Called "Don't Be Gone Too Long"|url=http://www.idolator.com/7508177/ariana-grande-duet-chris-brown-dont-be-gone-too-long|publisher=SpinMedia|date=2014-03-03|accessdate=2014-11-18|archive-date=2014-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141105172446/http://www.idolator.com/7508177/ariana-grande-duet-chris-brown-dont-be-gone-too-long|dead-url=no}}</ref>這支單曲原訂於2014年3月25日推出，不過卻因為克里斯小子涉嫌毆打被送入監獄而被延後。<ref name=":1">{{cite web|last=Wass|first=Mike|title=Chris Brown And Ariana Grande's Duet "Don't Be Gone Too Long" Has Been Postponed|url=http://www.idolator.com/7510240/chris-brown-ariana-grande-duet-postponed|publisher=SpinMedia|date=2014-03-17|accessdate=2014-11-18|archive-date=2014-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141018181543/http://www.idolator.com/7510240/chris-brown-ariana-grande-duet-postponed|dead-url=no}}</ref>格蘭德於2014年3月17日透過Twitter宣布這首歌的推延，她說道「我的摯愛……有些事情很明顯地在最近發生變化……因此，我們必須將〈Don't Be Gone Too Long〉的倒數延緩，有些事是我們無法控制的。」<ref name=":1" />她在當晚舉辦了一場現場直播，預先公開了她第二張專輯中的四首新歌，以彌補這張單曲的延誤。<ref>{{cite web|last=Inocencio|first=Marc|title=Ariana Grande Teases Four New Songs During LiveStream: Listen|url=http://www.ryanseacrest.com/2014/03/24/ariana-grande-teases-four-news-song-during-livestream-listen/|publisher=Ryan Seacrest Productions|access-date=2015-02-16|archive-date=2014-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140510030414/http://www.ryanseacrest.com/2014/03/24/ariana-grande-teases-four-news-song-during-livestream-listen/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Livesteam>{{cite web|last1=Garibaldi|first1=Christina|title=Ariana Grande Teases New Music In Livestream…And Everyone Missed It?|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1724688/ariana-grande-teases-new-music-in-livestreamand-everyone-missed-it/|website=MTV|date=2014-03-24|access-date=2015-02-16|archive-date=2020-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126074649/http://www.mtv.com/news/1724688/ariana-grande-teases-new-music-in-livestreamand-everyone-missed-it/|dead-url=no}}</ref>格蘭德在消息公布後兩天透漏，由於這首歌曲的延期，她將發行她即將推出的第二張專輯中的首支單曲作為替代。<ref>{{cite web|last=Grande|first=Ariana|title=now you'll be getting my 1st|url=https://twitter.com/ArianaGrande/status/446445506508898304|publisher=Twitter|access-date=2015-02-16|archive-date=2016-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310095938/https://twitter.com/arianagrande/status/446445506508898304|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Grande confirms Brown single is on hold|url=http://www.covermg.com/grande-confirms-brown-single-is-on-hold/|publisher=Think Agency|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140518025642/http://www.covermg.com/grande-confirms-brown-single-is-on-hold/|archivedate=2014-05-18}}</ref>她在2014年5月下旬完成了這張專輯的製作。<ref>{{cite web|title=Ariana Grande Is Completing Her Sophomore Album This Week|url=http://www.disneydreaming.com/2014/05/23/ariana-grande-is-completing-her-sophomore-album-this-week/|website=Disney Dreaming|date=2014-05-23|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714130149/http://www.disneydreaming.com/2014/05/23/ariana-grande-is-completing-her-sophomore-album-this-week/|archivedate=2014-07-14}}</ref>格蘭德在6月28日證實這張專輯名為《我的全部》，而將在2014年8月25日發行。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Peters|first1=Mitchell|title=Ariana Grande Announces Second Album 'My Everything,' Teases 'Break Free' Video|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6141064/ariana-grande-announces-second-album-my-everything-teases-break-free-zedd|website=Billboard|accessdate=2014-06-29|archive-date=2019-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190412154514/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6141064/ariana-grande-announces-second-album-my-everything-teases-break-free-zedd|dead-url=no}}</ref>這張專輯的包裝照片已在2014年5月27日拍攝完畢。<ref>{{cite web|title=Ariana Grande Teases “Problem” Music Video: It’s Coming Soon!|url=http://www.bopandtigerbeat.com/2014/05/ariana-grande-teases-problem-music-video-its-coming-soon/|website=[[虎韻|Tiger Beat]]|date=2014-05-28|access-date=2015-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150101213431/http://www.bopandtigerbeat.com/2014/05/ariana-grande-teases-problem-music-video-its-coming-soon/|archive-date=2015-01-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref>格蘭德表示她之所以選擇這個封面設計，是因為她認為「每首歌都有著強烈的主題，所以我只想要一個非常簡單的封面。因此我們可以在每首歌中創造出更多的視覺主題。」<ref name=ExclusiveContent>{{cite web|title=Ariana Grande Announces Exclusive Concert!|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NorphRjDAyc|website=Youtube|accessdate=2014-06-29|archive-date=2014-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140824184806/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NorphRjDAyc|dead-url=no}}</ref>

